text: Selena Barajas (born 22 January 1982) is a Mexican volleyball player. She played at the 2002 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, 2003 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2006 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2014 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for UANL Tigres. == References == == Other websites== * Selena Barajas - Mexico www.bvbinfo.com Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican volleyball players
